    "description": "◆虚假家庭生活中的一页日常<br><br>伊甸学园出了一份绘图日记作业给阿尼亚。<br>早上去学校上学，夜晚和家人团聚。<br>假日则全家一起去海边、水族馆等不同地方，收集可以用来画绘图日记的题材。<br>究竟阿尼亚能否顺利完成绘图日记呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170370/extras/161b92503a98d7c2a8d395bb692b8b65.poster.avif?t=1749605260\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170370/extras/161b92503a98d7c2a8d395bb692b8b65.webm?t=1749605260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>◆在各式各样的地方打造回忆，发现新奇事物就用相机拍下照片！<br>在福杰家和各个出游地点都充满着诸如蝴蝶、秋千等各式各样的新奇事物。发现时就用相机拍摄下来吧！<br>只要能拍出好照片，就能累积记录在绘图日记里的回忆。<br>出游地点包含公园、海滩、狗狗公园、水族馆、美术馆等一共10处！　　<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170370/extras/ba257eeddd5c94b45c9ed272ee0f4c67.poster.avif?t=1749605260\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170370/extras/ba257eeddd5c94b45c9ed272ee0f4c67.webm?t=1749605260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>◆15种以上“SPY×FAMILY 间谍过家家”独有的小游戏！<br>能够以小游戏的形式体验宛如“SPY×FAMILY 间谍过家家”般有点的古怪日常。收录了以动画中某个情境为主题的小游戏，或是本作独有的原创小游戏等等，总共15种以上 。<br>配合节奏与约尔进行特训，或是幻想乘坐在邦德身上玩间谍游戏，甚至还能运用阿尼亚的超能力看透对手的扑克牌手牌！？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170370/extras/27e2c023a4c62f80480f1facf8a94a2e.poster.avif?t=1749605260\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170370/extras/27e2c023a4c62f80480f1facf8a94a2e.webm?t=1749605260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>◆随自己喜好任意穿搭！<br>玩家能够为劳埃德、阿尼亚、约尔、邦德更换身上所穿的服饰。<br>本作独有的服装、饰品、发型等合计80种以上！<br>游玩小游戏来累积点数，就能利用这些点数在游戏里的商店购买服饰。<br>請盡情遊玩，然後买下各种服饰穿去出游吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170370/extras/b5de824747801de6287d11ab22b01a07.poster.avif?t=1749605260\" width=616 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170370/extras/b5de824747801de6287d11ab22b01a07.webm?t=1749605260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>◆个性丰富的角色们也会一一登场<br>阿尼亚、劳埃德、约尔、邦德自然不会缺席，伊甸学园的同班同学达米安和贝琪、约尔的弟弟尤里、WISE的女间谍〈夜帷〉 等多位熟悉的角色们亦会在游戏中登场。<br>在学校和同学们一起玩耍、上课，与家人及朋友们编织出一段段无可取代的时光。",
